descriptionHtml:
Discover the top discounts, flyers and coupons for your favourite stores with reebee! Save time and money on your shopping trips with the latest flyers, coupons, deals and discounts.

Experience the satisfaction of efficient shopping and smart savings with reebee! By carefully planning your grocery list and discovering great discounts, you'll effortlessly stock up on your favourite brands at unbeatable prices. Say goodbye to forgotten essentials and overspending; let reebee be your go-to tool for managing your shopping lists and making the most of your budget. Enjoy the feeling of accomplishment with every well-planned trip to the store!

Find the lowest local prices, the best coupons and top discounts to plan your shopping lists. reebee has current and upcoming flyers from hundreds of retailers across Canada, including Walmart, Costco, Sobeys, Metro, Shoppers Drug Mart, Save on Foods, Frescho, The Home Depot and more.

Download reebee for free today to discover thousands of coupons, discounts, and deals near you.

How reebee helps Canadians save time and money:
- Browse weekly flyers for deals, coupons and discounts. Save on every item on your shopping list – from turkey to toys to tools!
- View flyers by shopping category. Whether you need grocery, home improvement, auto, furniture, or pharmacy flyers or coupons, reebee’s flyer categories make it easy to find what you need.
- Shop deals & savings for Canada’s top stores: Walmart, Real Canadian Superstore, Super C, No Frills, The Home Depot, and more!
- View upcoming deals and flyers so you can plan for next week’s shopping trip
- Shop savings online! That’s right – you can use reebee flyers in-store or online! Simply click the “view or buy online” button to get shopping and saving without ever leaving your home.
- Save your favourite flyers from Walmart, Staples, Giant Tiger, Super C, The Home Depot & more stores in Canada.

Shop better with smart shopping lists
- Add everything you need for your grocery, home, pet, and electronics shopping needs. Our shopping list will even let you note how much of everything you need – so everyone gets their toothpaste tube or box of cookies!
- View items by price so you can make the most of your grocery budget
- Compare prices for items on your shopping list across stores in Canada like Walmart, Giant Tiger, Real Canadian Superstore, Shopper’s Drug Mart, or wherever you like to shop!
- See something in a flyer you like? You can save it to your shopping list! You’ll never have to worry about missing out on a great deal or forgetting something in the store.
- View items by their store to plan your shopping list. Whether you shop by price or by store, you can get the best savings and deals.

By shopping deals at top stores like Walmart, Canadian Tire, The Home Depot, Real Canadian Superstore, and more, you can always save money shopping online or in-store with reebee! Return to what matters and let reebee save you time and money during your shopping adventures.

Shop the best shopping deals now with flyers from the reebee flyers app! Keep your shopping list organized with our free shopping list creator. Start saving on your shopping list today!

title:
reebee: Flyers & Shopping List
54.0.0

creator: Flipp Operations Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Beat rising costs with weekly grocery shopping deals that help you save money using reebee. Browse the newest flyers from Canadian stores near you, create your grocery list, and search for ingredient to compare prices. Add items to your shopping list, and view flyers, deals, and coupons all in one place to help you save big.

reebee helps you find deals and coupons from hundreds of local grocery stores including:
- Walmart Canada
- Real Canadian Superstore
- Canadian Tire
- No Frills
- Costco
- Super C

And many more stores to help you price match groceries, create your shopping list, browse flyers, and get deal alerts. Not only does our shopping list help you save on groceries, but also on home & garden, pharmacy, general merchandise, and electronics.

Here’s how to shop smart with reebee:

Find nearby stores with your postal code or location.
- See the latest deals and compare grocery prices for your local stores
- Select your favourite stores like Walmart Canada, No Frills, Staples, Super C, and Canadian Tire to quickly access flyers in one place

Search for any item and start building your shopping list.
- Compare prices from different stores, right from search results
- Filter by favourite stores or ways to shop to find what you need faster

Clip or circle deals straight to your grocery list.
- Keep your shopping on track with a list of deals you’ve saved to your list, organized by store
- Price match at participating stores like No Frills and Giant Tiger with clippings from your reebee shopping list

Browse weekly flyers by category.
- View weekly deals on groceries, electronics, home & garden, and more
- Plan ahead with the Upcoming section that lets you preview deals

Create and share your shopping list.
- Add the items you need to your grocery list and reebee will show you deals for those items
- Plan your best shopping route with multiple shopping lists organized by store

Get notified when new deals arrive.
- Create a Watch List to track new deals for items over time
- Never miss a flyer drop or coupon from your favourite stores like Real Canadian Superstore, Giant Tiger, Canadian Tire, and more

Collect loyalty points and plan your shopping list.
- Add your store loyalty cards to reebee so you don’t miss out on points and rewards
- Have your rewards, flyers, coupons, and shopping list with you at all times to plan on-the-go

By following these simple steps, reebee helps you simplify your shopping routine. Ready to create your grocery list of giant savings? Plan with reebee’s digital shopping list and start finding the best grocery flyers to shop smart.

Simply put, reebee makes shopping and deal hunting simple with flyers, coupons, grocery lists, and fresh savings every single week. If you’re looking to save money in Canada, reebee is a must-have for grocery shopping with the best sales from all your favourite stores like Walmart Canada, Real Canadian Superstore, Giant Tiger, Super C, Staples, No Frills, and more!

Questions or suggestions? Contact us at https://help.reebee.com
descriptionShort: Save on groceries with deals, grocery lists & price matching in Canadian stores
